---
import LegalLayout from '../../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { SITE, LEGAL, CONTACT, PENDIENTE } from '../../lib/site';

const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<LegalLayout
  lang={lang}
  pageKey="legalNotice"
  title="Legal notice | Alma Mía"
  description="Legal notice of Alma Mía pursuant to the Spanish LSSI-CE: identifying details of the owner, terms of use of the website and intellectual property."
  h1="Legal notice"
  lastUpdated="14/06/2026"
>
  <p>
    In compliance with Article 10 of Spanish Law 34/2002 of 11 July, on Information Society
    Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSI-CE), the following identifying details of the owner
    of this website are provided.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Identifying details</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Owner:</strong> {LEGAL.titularName} {LEGAL.titularName === PENDIENTE && '(pending completion)'}</li>
    <li><strong>NIF/NIE:</strong> {LEGAL.nif}</li>
    <li><strong>Address:</strong> {LEGAL.address}</li>
    <li><strong>Email:</strong> {CONTACT.email}</li>
    <li><strong>Website:</strong> {SITE.url}</li>
    <li><strong>Trade name:</strong> {SITE.brand}</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    <em>The data marked as {PENDIENTE} must be completed with the owner's actual tax
    information before the site is published.</em>
  </p>

  <h2>2. Purpose</h2>
  <p>
    This legal notice governs access to, navigation of and use of the website {SITE.domain},
    through which {SITE.brand} provides information about its private chef services and
    in-home gastronomic experiences. Accessing the site implies acceptance of the conditions
    set out in this notice.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Terms of use</h2>
  <p>
    The user undertakes to make appropriate and lawful use of the website and its contents, in
    accordance with the applicable legislation, good faith and public order. The use of the site
    for unlawful purposes or purposes harmful to the owner or third parties is prohibited.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Intellectual and industrial property</h2>
  <p>
    All contents of the site (texts, photographs, design, logos, brand and code) are owned by
    {SITE.brand} or by third parties who have authorised their use, and are protected by
    intellectual and industrial property regulations. Their reproduction, distribution or
    transformation without express authorisation is prohibited.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Liability</h2>
  <p>
    The owner shall not be liable for damages arising from improper use of the site, nor for any
    interruptions, errors or omissions that may exist. The site may contain links to third-party
    pages over whose contents the owner assumes no responsibility.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Applicable law</h2>
  <p>
    This legal notice is governed by Spanish law. For the resolution of any dispute, the parties
    submit to the courts and tribunals that have jurisdiction in accordance with the law.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
